/1416941287.jpg\",\"group_3\":\"/uploads/goods/176/1416935746.jpg\"}','{}',1),(177,'湛江河唇红杨桃','水果','','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/goods/177/1416936512.jpg\" /></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/goods/177/1416936518.jpg\" /></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/goods/177/1416936526.jpg\" /></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/goods/177/1416936539.jpg\" /></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/goods/177/1416936545.jpg\" /></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n','广东','2500g',48.00,'一村一品','http://item.taobao.com/item.htm?spm=a230r.1.14.113.AZpCTp&id=36494640586&ns=1&abbucket=3#detail','{\"group_1\":\"/uploads/goods/177/1416936364.jpg\",\"group_2\":\"/uploads/goods/177/1416936366.jpg\",\"group_3\":\"/uploads/goods/177/1416936475.jpg\",\"group_4\":\"/uploads/goods/177/1416936480.jpg\",\"small\":\"/uploads/goods/177/1416936377.jpg\",\"medium\":\"/uploads/goods/177/1416936379.jpg\"}','{}',1),(178,'增城贝贝小南瓜','蔬菜','','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/goods/178/1416937009.jpg\" style=\"height:860px; width:750px\" /></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/goods/178/1416937019.jpg\" /></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/goods/178/1416937025.jpg\" style=\"height:872px; width:750px\" /></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/goods/178/1416937034.jpg\" /></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/goods/178/1416937041.jpg\" style=\"height:995px; width:750px\" /></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/goods/178/1416937047.jpg\" style=\"height:779px; width:750px\" /></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n','广东 广州','2500g ',48.80,'一村一品','http://item.ny.taobao.com/item.htm?spm=a1z10.1.w4004-1593632664.30.D0mhBj&id=35337532866','{\"group_1\":\"/uploads/goods/178/1416936913.jpg\",\"group_2\":\"/uploads/goods/178/1416936915.jpg\",\"group_3\":\"/uploads/goods/178/1416936916.jpg\",\"group_4\":\"/uploads/goods/178/1416936918.jpg\",\"small\":\"/uploads/goods/178/1416936920.jpg\",\"medium\":\"/uploads/goods/178/1416936923.jpg\"}','{}',1),(179,'增城迟菜心','蔬菜','','<p>增城迟菜心，又名菜树、树菜（听老辈人说，以前迟菜心还未出名的时候，广州城里的人来增城看到这种高大似小树的巨型菜心，以为怪物，都不敢吃），也有人称高脚菜心，其实高脚菜心还有两种，一种叫鹩哥俐，一种则是由鹩哥俐与迟菜心杂交后的半吊子迟菜心，都不能算是真正的迟菜心。根据上市时间，真正的迟菜心一般要11月后才能上市，较早上市的都是刚才提到的另两种高脚菜心。天气越冷，菜心越甜，这也是迟菜心的特点之一。</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;迟菜心一般要经过90至120天左右才能收割，比一般菜心要迟，所以称为迟菜心，一般的菜心一棵不过50克重，而迟菜心每棵可重达500克以上，叶子长度可达一米，非常巨大。其最大的特点是菜质鲜嫩，快炒香脆甜爽，慢煮软嫩可口，风味独特，营养丰富，含有丰富的维生素，钙，锌等多种营养成份。具有稀释、清除肠道毒素，改善便秘，预防肠癌，美容保健，改善身体机能，增强免疫力的功效。晒成的菜干更是上乘的汤料，汤味甘醇，菜香特浓，具有清心润肺，去热解毒的药效。</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;迟菜心以增城小楼镇内产为最佳，增城的小楼镇一带生产的菜心，才是地道的迟菜心。小楼镇地处北回归线，这里的地质特殊，这里的菜心长如菜树，能长到一米高，但却依然皮脆肉软，茎肥叶厚，煮炒快熟，吃之甜美，很有菜味，非一般菜心可比，因此，迟菜心被食家们誉为&ldquo;菜王&rdquo;。由于小楼镇区域不大，因此，迟菜心的产量是不大的，加上如此受欢迎，价格自然比一般菜心高。</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;要说明一下的是，我们以有机农家肥料为主，杀虫剂使用次数少（说完全不用那是骗人的，不然那么长的生长期，虫子都把叶子吃光啦），保证产品的质量上乘。</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><br />\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/goods/179/1416937604.jpg\" /></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/goods/179/1416937616.jpg\" /></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/goods/179/1416937627.jpg\" /></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/goods/179/1416937640.jpg\" /></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/goods/179/1416937654.jpg\" /></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/goods/179/1416937702.jpg\" /></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/goods/179/1416937710.jpg\" /></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/goods/179/1416937718.jpg\" /></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/goods/179/1416937724.jpg\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/goods/179/1416937732.jpg\" /></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/goods/179/1416937738.jpg\" /></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\n','广东 广州','4000g',88.00,'一村一品','http://item.taobao.com/item.htm?spm=a230r.1.14.1.7Yv9Sy&id=15039952793&ns=1&abbucket=3#detail','{\"group_1\":\"/uploads/goods/179/1416937383.jpg\",\"group_2\":\"/uploads/goods/179/1416937385.jpg\",\"group_3\":\"/uploads/goods/179/1416937388.jpg\",\"group_4\":\"/uploads/goods/179/1416937389.jpg\",\"small\":\"/uploads/goods/179/1416937396.jpg\",\"medium\":\"/uploads/goods/179/1416937398.jpg\",\"large\":\"/uploads/goods/179/1416941036.jpg\"}','{}',1),(180,'清远连州甜菜心','蔬菜','','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/goods/180/1416938380.jpg\" style=\"height:600px; width:755px\" /></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/goods/180/1416938388.jpg\" style=\"height:585px; width:760px\" /></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/goods/180/1416938396.jpg\" style=\"height:566px; width:755px\" /></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/goods/180/1416938403.jpg\" style=\"height:566px; width:755px\" /></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/goods/180/1416938411.jpg\" style=\"height:566px; width:755px\" /></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/goods/180/1416938418.jpg\" style=\"height:566px; width:755px\" /></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/goods/180/1416938426.jpg\" style=\"height:566px; width:755px\" /></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/goods/180/1416938433.jpg\" /></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/goods/180/1416938443.jpg\" style=\"height:566px; width:755px\" /></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/goods/180/1416938450.jpg\" style=\"height:435px; width:755px\" /></p>\n\n<p style=\"t